module MiniC-LexAndCFSyntax-testcases

language MiniC
start symbol FormalList

//positive test cases
test empty list   [[]] parse succeeds
test int          [[int a]] parse succeeds
test double array [[float a[] ]] parse succeeds
test struct       [[struct a b]] parse succeeds

test more than 1 element [[int a, int b]] parse succeeds

//negative test cases

test missing type        [[a, b]] parse fails
test missing type        [[int a, b]] parse fails
test missing comma       [[int a int b]] parse fails
test only comma          [[, ]] parse fails
test missing parameter   [[int a,]] parse fails
test missing parameter   [[, int a]] parse fails
test invalid array usage [[int a[5] ]] parse fails